1. ❌ 404 Errors Fix karna
Jo pages exist nahi karte → unhe proper 404 status code dena
Ya important ho toh redirect (301) karna
2. 📄 Sitemap banana
sitemap.xml create/update karna
Usko Google Search Console me submit karna
3. 🏷️ Page Titles fix karna
Har page ka unique title likhna
Keywords add karna (SEO ke liye)
4. ✍️ Meta Description add karna
Har page me proper description likhna (Google me show hota hai)
5. 🔗 Canonical Tag set karna
Duplicate pages ko avoid karna
<link rel="canonical"> properly set karna
6. 🧱 Headings (H1, H2) set karna
Har page me:
1 H1
Proper H2, H3 structure
7. 🧠 Schema Markup add karna
Website ka type batana (Google ko samajhne ke liye)
Example:
Local Business
Insurance schema
8. ⚡ Website Speed improve karna
Images compress karna
Code optimize karna
Load time fast karna
9. 🤖 robots.txt banana
Google ko batana:
Kaunsa page crawl kare
Kaunsa ignore kare
10. 📱 OpenGraph Tags add karna
Jab link share ho (Facebook/WhatsApp):
Title
Image
Description sahi aaye